  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A literature-review survey of published hemolysis correlations was used to support the hemolysis model-form factor. The review synthesised findings from 14 peer-reviewed studies and is presented as the primary validation evidence for model-form adequacy.",
