    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the model for the stated COU on the basis that the literature review provided sufficient corroborating evidence of model-form adequacy across a broad range of published centrifugal pump studies. The team noted that achieved credibility levels are below required levels for several factors but concluded that the convergent body of published evidence compensates for the absence of dedicated experimental validation. Remaining factor gaps are acknowledged as epistemic limitations to be addressed in subsequent assessment cycles.",
